div.p: Molecular Systems Physiology Group, University of Galway, Ireland. https://thielelab.eu
This is a metabolism reconstruction of:Methanobrevibacter smithii ATCC 35061
The draft reconstruction was created using Kbase/ModelSeed and refined with the DEMETER pipeline from the COBRA toolbox v3
When using or adapting this reconstruction, please cite:

Heinken, A., Hertel, J., Acharya, G., Ravcheev, D.A., Nyga, M., Okpala, O.E., Hogan, M., Magnusdottir, S., Martinelli, F., Nap, B., Preciat, G., Edirisinghe, J.N., Henry, C.S., Fleming, R.M.T., Thiele, I., "AGORA2: Knowledge-driven genome-scale reconstruction of 7,302 human microbes for personalised medicine", Nat Biotech (2023), https://doi.org/10.1101/2020.11.09.375451.
